---
// Hero Section based on crawled 10botics.com data
// This was originally an Elementor slides widget with 4 slides
---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img 
      src="/images/WhatsApp-Image-2024-09-10-at-11.15.43-AM.jpeg" 
      alt="STEM Education Background" 
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600/90 to-blue-800/90"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center">
      <!-- Main Heading -->
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        專注 STEM 課程研發及教學
      </h1>
      
      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-blue-100 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        教材及課程是由我們專業 STEM 團隊開發，提供創新及完整的學習體驗
      </p>
      
      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
        <a 
          href="/school-courses" 
          class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"
        >
          STEM 課程概覽
        </a>
        <a 
          href="/contact-us" 
          class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors"
        >
          聯絡我們
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Course Highlights Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-16">
        <!-- Donkey Car -->
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Donkey Car</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">自駕車編程課程</p>
          <a href="/school-courses/donkey-car" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white text-sm mt-2 inline-block">
            了解更多 →
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- KSP -->
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">KSP</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">航天工程課程</p>
          <a href="/school-courses/ksp" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white text-sm mt-2 inline-block">
            了解更多 →
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Raspberry Pi -->
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Raspberry Pi</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">物聯網編程課程</p>
          <a href="/school-courses/raspberry-pi" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white text-sm mt-2 inline-block">
            了解更多 →
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Minecraft -->
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Minecraft</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-100">遊戲設計課程</p>
          <a href="/school-courses/minecraft" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white text-sm mt-2 inline-block">
            了解更多 →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, white 2px, transparent 2px), radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, white 2px, transparent 2px); background-size: 50px 50px;"></div>
  </div>
</section> 